com.ge.dspmicro.hoover.api.processor

Interface IProcessor


  • public interface IProcessor
    An optional component injected to a Spillway to manipulate the data passed in according to the process type defined. The manipulated data will be send out to the destination specified.

    • Method Summary

      Methods

        Manipulate the data passed in according to the process type defined and send out the result to the destination.
